{"tid":53180,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺肥婆全部應該攞去人道毀滅","createTime":"2016-12-24T13:40:31.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-26T02:04:52.000Z","uid":48750,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c233dee05c42a3f66a2ae272b1f7299ae9c92f96","tid":53180,"uid":48750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T13:40:31.000Z","msg":"是咁的 最近發覺<br />\n肥婆都係自撚私 偷食肉 把口賤過地底泥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都係理應死全家 特別係教畜 廢中 廢老<br />\n睇見妳沈重的脂肪 <br />\n已經係上天對妳既懲罰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個樣靚都話冇咁反感 <br />\n但多數十個十點九個都係成隻豬咁樣<br />\n食野都會發出豬食野既燥音<br />\n進食時毫無儀態 禮貌 仲衰過支那人<br />\n唔知係咪新界啲農場偷走出黎既豬<br />\n然後當街老強中出一個肥婆 衍生出黎既怪物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌過肥婆既男人更加係不得好死<br />\n咁多瘦底 大波 長腿唔屌 竟然去屌肥婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n對唔對得住自己既父母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係諗起個畫面隔夜飯都嘔埋出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌肥婆同屌米芝連人有乜分別 <br />\n望住一條條車軚都扯得起？ <br />\nsorry 我真係接受唔撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n應該將所有肥婆攞去人道毀滅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw 平安夜快樂 <br />\n毒撚當然安全留在家中 出Post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n認同請正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔認同請回上一頁"},{"pid":"2251897c191f4ca0210791b2163ca04e75a956fb","tid":53180,"uid":6745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T13:42:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2847f5af6c5a21a217b3231aad86c81b9c35e805","tid":53180,"uid":48750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T13:50:58.000Z","msg":"打漏左 肥婆既陪葬品係一枝美極<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15759043ef682be2748df3a2a79abd4fb956f8ef","tid":53180,"uid":22927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T14:01:15.000Z","msg":"將肥婆人道毀滅浪費毒針<br />\n拎去堆填令堆填區急速飽和<br />\n焚化又污染空氣<br />\n極力要求各大國家合作整火箭<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">將肥婆射上太空</span></span>"},{"pid":"b5da2cd88fb0fdb4dc814f2b2cfb235cb6020bb0","tid":53180,"uid":25444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T14:02:21.000Z","msg":"人道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n梗係直接毀滅啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ad478348b4b80277e1ac9b3a1ed833b08db60a7","tid":53180,"uid":48750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T15:07:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>將肥婆人道毀滅浪費毒針<br />\n拎去堆填令堆填區急速飽和<br />\n焚化又污染空氣<br />\n極力要求各大國家合作整火箭<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">將肥婆射上太空</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n將肥婆帶去火星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"></span>"},{"pid":"f0b2740aaea07305c744551332529cfe8ff8125d","tid":53180,"uid":53602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T17:31:04.000Z","msg":"肥婆好無品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n肥婆同人一齊食飯會夾走人哋嘅餸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c06a3d7e134e766ae5d46a5ad98af3ccde6271ea","tid":53180,"uid":48750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T02:01:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>肥婆好無品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n肥婆同人一齊食飯會夾走人哋嘅餸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hk